title: Netherlands : top 10 online stores

summary: The Netherlands top Online in the online stores was Online wehkamp.nl , who made 1410.2 revenue .
The most top Online was apple.com , with just 168.9 revenue .

In second place was Online coolblue.nl with 1110.7 revenue ; third place went to Online bol.com with 1410.2 revenue ; fourth place went to Online alternate.nl with 168.9 revenue and fifth place went to Online ah.nl , who was 485.8 revenue .
gold: The biggest online stores in the Netherlands include domestic players like online hypermarket bol.com , electronics retailer coolblue.nl and fashion store wehkamp.nl , sometimes outperforming major e-commerce companies such as Amazon or Zalando .
